OL,3,CRecord number of homeless people died
OL,4,Cin 2024, figures suggest
OL,6,FThe number of people who died while
OL,7,Fhomeless rose to a record high last
OL,8,Fyear, according to new data.
OL,10,FThe Museum of Homelessness said its
OL,11,Fresearch registered at least 1,611
OL,12,Fdeaths in 2024, including 11 children.
OL,14,FThis was up from 1,474 deaths in 2023
OL,15,Fand 1,313 deaths in 2022.
