OL,6,FThe Museum of Homelessness has been
OL,7,Frunning the Dying Homeless Project
OL,8,Fsince 2019 and gathers its data each
OL,9,Fyear through Freedom of Information
OL,10,Frequests, coroner inquests and
OL,11,Fmemorials submitted by bereaved family
OL,12,Fmembers.
OL,14,FIt said overall, 44% of all the deaths
OL,15,Fin their data were drug and alcohol-
OL,16,Frelated.
