OL,3,CRecord number of homeless people died
OL,4,Cin 2024, figures suggest
OL,6,FWhile rough sleeping is most
OL,7,Fassociated with homelessness, living
OL,8,Fin temporary accommodation such as bed
OL,9,Fand breakfasts, hostels or other short-
OL,10,Fterm housing organised by a local
OL,11,Fauthority is also a form of
OL,12,Fhomelessness.
OL,14,FAccording to research by the Museum of
OL,15,FHomelessness, there were 11 children -
OL,16,Fthose aged younger than 18 -included
OL,17,Fin last year's data, of which four
OL,18,Fwere babies who had not yet reached
OL,19,Ftheir first birthday.
