OL,6,FThe number of children who died in
OL,7,F2024 was up from four in 2023.
OL,9,FAcross the UK's four nations, there
OL,10,Fwere 1,142 deaths in England, 211 in
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland, 168 in Scotland and
OL,12,F90 in Wales.
OL,14,FTotal deaths in Scotland and Wales
OL,15,Ffell year-on-year, but Northern
OL,16,FIreland and England both had increases.
