OL,6,FGill Taylor from The Museum of
OL,7,FHomelessness said: "Whilst it is
OL,8,Fpositive that local authorities and
OL,9,Fsafeguarding adult boards appear to be
OL,10,Ftaking the issue more seriously, with
OL,11,Fbetter reporting and evidence of
OL,12,Fimproved local partnership working to
OL,13,Fprevent deaths, turning the tide on
OL,14,Fthis enormous loss of life needs more
OL,15,Fthan better counting.
OL,17,F"We remember with love all those who
OL,18,Fdied and continue our work in
OL,19,Fsolidarity with bereaved loved ones
OL,20,Fand the homeless community."
